user.biography: We develop and publish mobile games and millions of people play them all over the world.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on September 10, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'VFX Artist PLAYGENDARY'.

node.text:
Our aim is to create fun projects, that’s why we pay special attention to special effects. VFX Artists are in charge of this work. They shoot the fireworks in the result screen in Flow Legends, activate boosters at the level end of Design Masters and blow the bombs in Escape Masters 💥
⠀
VFX Artists create the effects, optimize, polish and import them to Unity. The guys work with passion for details and can show the process physics using particle systems. They also know the animation principles, can create shaders and even 2D or 3D model.
⠀
And yep — we have VFX vacancies, look for them on our website 😉
⠀
—
⠀
Мы хотим делать фановые проекты, поэтому уделяем особое внимание эффектам. Их у нас делают VFX-артисты. Это они запускают салюты на экране результатов в Flow Legends, активируют неизрасходованные бустеры в конце уровня в Design Masters и взрывают бомбы в Escape Masters 💥
⠀
VFX-артисты создают эффекты, оптимизируют, полишат до идеала и импортируют в Unity. Ребята работают с любовью к деталям и умеют передавать физику процессов, используя системы частиц. А еще знают принципы анимаций, умеют создавать шейдеры и даже сделать 2D или 3D модель.
⠀
И да, по этому направлению есть вакансии — ищите на нашем сайте 😉

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on September 01, 2021. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Hey! It’s been a while! 👀
⠀
We threw ourselves in development (including projects in genres which are new for us — details coming soon) and forgot to share news and plans. The injustice to be corrected, stay tuned for our posts.
⠀
Coming event — on September 4 and 5 we are going to the Animators Meet in Moscow, Russia. 60 kilos of merch, several tablets with our games and plenty of networking included. Look for our stand, we’ll be glad to see you 😉
⠀
—
⠀
Привет. Давно не виделись! 👀
⠀
С головой ушли в разработку проектов (в том числе, в новых для нас жанрах — скоро подробности) и забыли делиться новостями и планами. Будем исправлять эту несправедливость, так что следите за постами.
⠀
Из ближайшего — 4 и 5 сентября едем на «Слёт аниматоров» в Москве. С собой 60 кг мерча, несколько планшетов с нашими играми и много нетворкинга. Ищите наш стенд, будем рады увидеться 😉

node.text:
Мы ищем опытного продюсера с критичным взглядом и желанием создавать крутые Casual-проекты! 
⠀
Если это про тебя, то читай подробности на сайте и отправляй резюме: playgendary.com/careers/producer
⠀
А если ты знаешь, кто бы идеально подошел на эту роль, то отправляй его контакты на hr@playgendary.com. За успешную рекомендацию мы выплачиваем денежный бонус.

You can keep active spirits up even remotely. We have moved all of the company activities to our team members’ homes – including the workouts. ⠀
⠀
Fitness programs were always off the charts. Now the new hit is our online yoga with a trainer! 🧘🏻‍♂️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on March 31, 2020. May be an image of text that says 'TEAMPLAY CAN CHANGE THE WORLD SUPPORT THE ONES WHO NEED HELP'.

node.text:
In global response to COVID-19 we’ve donated 100,000 BYN to support the fight against the virus in the Republic of Belarus. Now is the time to take care of the others, not only of yourself. ⠀
⠀ ⠀
All our employees have already been asked to work from home, we’ve cancelled all the business trips, and we’re watching the situation closely. Please #stayhome if it’s possible – only together we’ll be able to overcome the challenges we face.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on March 29, 2020. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
Now it's crucial to take care of yourself and your close ones. That’s why recently we sent home even those who prefer working in the offices. ⠀ ⠀
⠀ ⠀ ⠀
When you’re a part of remote team the whole world is the place to create games.🎮❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on March 29, 2020. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
When having a meeting with your project team. ⠀

We’ve been creating games from different cities as a remote team for a long time. And we know for sure how important it’s to support each other distantly. Take care during these difficult times and remember no distance can stop you, if you love what you do ♥️

node.text:
Do u remember the times when phones had no touchscreens?
⠀
It’s amazing how fast everything develops. Let’s remember old-school games 🕹

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on February 13, 2020. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
There’ll be 117 new emojis in the 2nd half of 2020, but u can already check them out. Some are hidden in the pic🕵️‍♂️
⠀
Spoiler: seven of them

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Playgendary on January 31, 2020. May be an image of text that says 'LINKEDIN FACEBOOK INSTAGRAM TINDER'.

node.text:
Where’s the snail? 🐌
⠀
We haven’t been able to find our snail since New Year, it seems to be stolen by the aliens.
⠀
Could u help us? ’Cause we’re starting to worry 👽

We burst into new week 🚀
They say Monday is a hard day, but we know how to make it better. Delicious coffee is a good option to start with ☕
